40492>>>
40492>>>        // if this view is being used in multiple contexts, you may need a block of code
40492>>>        // like this to handle customizations. This would include hiding rows and buttons
40492>>>        // (WebSet pbRender) and changing the values of various captions.
40492>>>        
40492>>>        String sDesdeDondeVengo
40492>>>        Case Begin
40492>>>            Case (NavigateData.eNavigateType=nfFromParent)
40494>>>                // If from parent, this is a constrained drill down.
40494>>>                // If needed you could check NavigateData.iTable to determine the constraining parent.
